title: Two in a Million - DocyReality- Rare Medical Condition People Me
description:
Two in a Million - DocyReality- Rare Medical Condition People Meet (2016) S01E01 small mp4 400p

Imagine living with one of the rarest medical conditions in the world; having no one to confide in who understands the pain, struggles, and isolation of everyday life. In each episode two people who share the same medical struggles meet and spend one week together, sharing hardships and incredible triumphs, visiting world-renowned doctors, and finding answers to important questions. This new series follows the powerful journey of those who live with some of the worldâ€™s most unusual disorders, and brings unique insight into the intimate journey of these extraordinary people. The connections they make are powerful beyond imagination
